sequenceDiagram
  box rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.65) Presentation Layer
    actor U as Admin/User
    participant UI as Projects UI
  end

  box rgba(236, 253, 245, 0.65) Application/API Layer
    participant API as Worker Projects API
    participant AUTH as Auth/RBAC
    participant SCOPE as Tenant Scope
    participant PRJSVC as Project Service
  end

  box rgba(245, 243, 255, 0.65) Data Layer
    participant DB as D1 project tables
    participant AUD as audit_log
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2
  end

  U->>UI: Nhập project header
  UI->>API: POST /api/projects
  API->>AUTH: Verify session and MANAGE_PROJECTS
  AUTH-->>API: authorized
  API->>SCOPE: Resolve tenant/company scope
  SCOPE-->>API: tenantId companyId
  Note over SCOPE,DB: Project, workflow, evidence and activity rows are written in the same tenant/company scope.
  API->>PRJSVC: Validate project data
  PRJSVC->>DB: Validate source warehouse in scope

  alt Invalid data or cross-scope warehouse
    DB-->>PRJSVC: not found or invalid
    PRJSVC-->>API: 400/404
    API-->>UI: show error no project
  else Valid project
    PRJSVC->>DB: INSERT projects
    PRJSVC->>DB: INSERT default workflow stages
    PRJSVC->>DB: INSERT project_activity
    PRJSVC->>AUD: INSERT CREATE_PROJECT
    API-->>UI: 201 project id
    UI->>API: GET /api/projects/:id
    API->>DB: SELECT project detail stages tasks in scope
    DB-->>API: project detail
    API-->>UI: render project detail
  end

  opt Upload evidence after create
    UI->>API: POST /api/projects/:id/evidence
    API->>AUTH: Verify MANAGE_PROJECTS
    API->>SCOPE: Check project in scope
    API->>R2: PUT evidence object
    API->>DB: INSERT project_evidence metadata
    API->>DB: INSERT project_activity
    API-->>UI: evidence metadata
  end
